reviewText: Love these classic movies and for such a great price!
All three of these titles are available on Google Play for you Chromecast users out there!
Used to watch all 3 of these movies when I was young (born 1988) and now my daughter can enjoy them on DVD!!! Very Exciting!

Was great to have these classics at together! My kids each had
One of  these three as favorites and now i can share them.with my
Grandkids.

Ferngully is hands down my favorite movie from my childhood and The Secret of Nihm is one of my husband's favorites. Neither of us had watched the other but for that price this bundle is a steal even with an unknown.
We got two movies we had never seen and one that we loved as kids. Now we can Share with our children!
I bought this for my daughter who absolutely loves it. She is in her 20s but remembers it fondly from watching as a youngster. Great memories never fade!
